com.hw4.Utku

Class GTUBinarySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hw4.Utku.BinaryTree<E>
      • com.hw4.Utku.GTUBinarySearchTree<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Type of value in tree. **Needs to be Comparable.

    public class GTUBinarySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends BinaryTree<E>
    This class is a binary tree representation of general trees in java. Every node can have multiple children. It implements toString() method and prints the tree in pre order traversal.
